{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7af024d362","title":"关于“教育方针”的言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"64c5f0bf81","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7af024d362"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d0fe9c9b0e","name":"厦门大学师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b8cba49330","type":"title","text":"关于“教育方针”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"e88c25b2c8","type":"authors","text":"厦门大学师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"545a823813","type":"paragraph","text":"张鸣镛：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"f4fd22b0a5","type":"paragraph","text":"“党提出的‘全面发展，因材施教’的教育方针是错误的，教员联系学生是‘不务正业’，这次反右派斗争学生来揭发先生的反党反社会主义谬论，是使先生难以‘全面负责’！”(厦大快报17期)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"944e23a3a9","type":"paragraph","text":"物理系郑碧生：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"faaee8e5c9","type":"paragraph","text":"“我不同意做一个红色专家，只要做一个淡红色的就够了。应先专后红。人的精力有限，所能学的是一个常数，多学政治就要少学专业，‘全面发展’会使业余精通成为不可能，象华罗庚这样天才的人物不会再有。有了专业就能做好一切工作，能解决一切问题，那时候党就要巴结我的。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"a87c9d20f4","type":"paragraph","text":"物理系黄席棠教授：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"f1d002fb36","type":"paragraph","text":"（对为工农兵开门的方针很抵触，对于高教部规定优先招收工农学生的规定很不满，很气愤的向高教部提意见。）“解放后学生的质量不如抗战前”，“现在的教育制度培养不出钱学森来！”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"},{"id":"c3588993be","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：中共厦门大学委员会宣传部编印《右派反动言论集》，1957年9月20日。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362"}],"page":{"id":"7ad21af7a3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7af024d362","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}